8 Reconns or rurs

Martis quintum vizt diem mensis Maii proxime futurum vel alium diem citra, si opus fuerit, istis horis et loco, reservavit. Necnon convocationem sive Synodum provincialem proximam usque ad et in eundem diem seu aliquem diem citra, si oporteat, istis horis ct loco, continuavit et prorogavit. Et monuit omnes et singulos nunc interessentes adhuc rursus comparendum, ad ulterius procedendum in dicta Convocntione sive Synodo, prout natura et qualitas ejusdem de se exigunt et requirunt, prout patet ex tenore schedulae inde per dominum Reverendissimum patrem lectae.

This Convocation, April, 1640, coincided with “The Short Parliament‚” summoned in consequence oi the rupture between England and Scotland‚ an outbreak known as “the first Bishops' War.”
